Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mine{lunch}, and this is Onii-chan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll really be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late. This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I praise my daughter for still making lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To outfox Tendou{IIRC he was the macho teacher}, you mustn't be late for at least three more days.{IIRC Tendou and Onii-chan bet about not being late.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:37.20,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,240)\fs26\fnArtificeSSK\bord0\c&H272BB6&\be2}Here\N comes\N Botsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch. You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you wake me up more gently?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? If you're late,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to clean the {school's }bathrooms every day until summer vacation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That Tendou bastard hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also at fault for responding to his provocations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes a man has to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,even in adverse conditions, Yui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.82,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\fad(0,250)}Sign: Yasohachi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou Makoto, you're a loser,\N just like I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep your word, even for one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou Makoto is hiding behind a girl's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A good chance for a photo!{His signature phrase "shutter chance"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they managed\N to make it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps{what would a rich kid call his old butler?}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, young master Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the top of the car has collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, you should say roof{saying "roof" in ENG}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of that disgraceful crap,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and have the roof repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't walk in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were riding a bike with Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan.
