Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of unexpected encounters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.77,Background,,0,0,0,,{いづれの御時にか、}In a certain reign,{First line from "Genji Monogatari - Kiritsubo"}{Literally "I can't tell which Emperor was ruling"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:34.23,Background,,0,0,0,,{女御、更衣あまたさぶらひたまひけるなかに}among all the daughters of both high-ranking and low-ranking nobles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.06,Background,,0,0,0,,{いとやんごとなき際にはあらぬが}someone of no great rank enjoyed exceptional favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The idol star, Maijima Karen-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is my classmate, believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She started working in show business at the age of eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,she rarely comes to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So she has almost no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was I sleeping at the front gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.67,Background,,0,0,0,,{いよいよあかずあはれなるものに思ほして}The Emperor felt deeply sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.14,Background,,0,0,0,,{人の譏りをもえ憚らせ給はず}His Highness ignored his other consorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:25.38,Background,,0,0,0,,{世の例にもなりぬべき御もてなしなり}He loved her so much that people felt he was setting a bad example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard Yoshiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.23,Background,,0,0,0,,Kondou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you read from that point?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Page 32, third line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your book is upside down, Kondou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As for today's after-school academic and career counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll start with Maijima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry to the cafeteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Onii-chan went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could have lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky. I'm the only one listening to her song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the wind blows and flips up her skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,i-it will be an exciting moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A close-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A good chance for a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hi. So you {\i1}were{\i0\fscx150} {\r}here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You quarreled with your manager,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and you didn't get your lunch money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like Hikari-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that's my manager's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari-san takes care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've suddenly started to hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she'll pick me up after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You're having a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have my lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate a lot of bread after second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'd rather let you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach is too honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we share it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This octopus{shaped wiener} is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to photograph a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you woke up early today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Misako-san, where's Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose she's taking a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui? Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan? You woke up early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, about lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have classes until noon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought we wouldn't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my lunch that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some time left.\N I'll hurry and make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then can you make more than yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been eating my lunches in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still both children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Karen-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you had to wait a while for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Delays can be quite lengthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're exhausting. I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having a good time on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like I'm having a good time when I'm doing things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? If this is a diversion for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But your fans might hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. My fans are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Some, though, want to take panty shots up my skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have a normal school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I get envious when I watch my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be enjoying nice, normal, teenage lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think that {\i1}you{\i0\fscx150} {\r}contribute to our teenage lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You make us dream of being famous like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We all adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you give us encouragement too. That's why we can keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to keep going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit cold, even though it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, this is a ticket to my live program tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a token of appreciation for lunch. Please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll definitely be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you were, Karen-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should tell me where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize to the director and the rest of the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back to school to hand in your paper
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for academic and career counseling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fan of Karen-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not! I'm her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I see you at her concerts and at the TV studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, I'm a fan too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I'm... I'm not just a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd be rejected.
