Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, where have you been?
