Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't wearing his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A troubled boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Plato,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trouble makes everyone grow up"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, could you give this back to Kondou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And give him my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Onii-chan's jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she the idol Maijima Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, did you know that Makoto-kun had such a famous friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just our classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, after that wild song,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's welcome the No.1 singer with the innocent and pure image,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maijima Karen-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming even more beautiful these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of female fans too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a saying that women become beautiful when they're in love.
