Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll pay dearly for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou Makoto, are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A perverted teacher!
