Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A good chance for a photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:01.60,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\fad(0,40)}Sign: Aniki (big brother)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any principles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou Makoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you have one more day to show that you can be on time for a full week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What's wrong?
