Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.53,0:18:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The new song you sang on stage the other day was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But I got a scolding afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to say, "No, I don't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you introduce me to a prince on a white horse?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idol with an image of purity and innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd known where you were sitting, I would've sung to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, aren't you coming to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be busy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, this is confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a photo shoot next Monday at Yasohachi Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you have school that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, you should go to bed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a hard schedule tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll pick you up at five in the morning. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}All right. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
