Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. The next photo is a sexy pose with the setting sun behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to wait for sunset. Let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why a sexy swimsuit picture now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After that live TV program, Karen's innocent image is a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And my boss is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to promote her with a different image.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she has great proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sexy despite her innocent appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you flirt with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be able to get a sexier shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's all right with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'll go for a super sexy shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your usual tactics?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like, "Isn't it cold?\N Would you like a cup of hot tea?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I getting photographed in {\i1}this{\i0\fscx50} {\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go in the cold sea wearing just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can succeed without doing things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a bit cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a cup of hot tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you going to use that tactic on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for Karen-chan.
