Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Chase after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The thing is, the key is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The key for this one is also missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
