Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.78,0:24:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.27,0:24:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.76,0:24:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see your naked body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.26,0:24:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Mister Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, Karen-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel you inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.12,0:25:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.58,0:25:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.79,0:25:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.07,0:26:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after that, Karen-chan flew to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.04,0:26:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dramatic escape made her boss realize how determined she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.13,0:26:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He agreed that she could study abroad to become a proper stage singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.80,0:26:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of a sex star.
