Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.69,0:26:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.09,0:26:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.20,0:26:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah, but wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.90,0:26:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.97,0:26:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Tomomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.41,0:26:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she with Yoshiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.42,0:26:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. She's acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.48,0:26:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's not herself these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.73,0:26:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to poke your nose in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.33,0:26:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm just being kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.50,0:26:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.38,0:27:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.60,0:27:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Kondou Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.52,0:27:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding double is illegal!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.51,0:27:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding double is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.85,0:27:07.51,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.02,0:27:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.00,0:27:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn playboy. Yui-san is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.24,0:27:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.49,0:27:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.71,0:27:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.62,0:27:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun, help me.
